  "prompt": "Which is best IT institute in Delhi?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" IT institute in Delhi can be subjective and may depend on various factors such as the specific courses you're interested in, faculty quality, infrastructure, placement opportunities, and personal preferences. However, some of the well-regarded IT institutes in Delhi include:\n\n1. **NIIT Delhi**: Known for its wide range of IT courses and strong industry connections.\n\n2. **Aptech Computer Education**: Offers various IT and software courses with good placement support.\n\n3. **Jetking**: Focuses on hardware and networking courses with practical training.\n\n4. **CETPA Infotech**: Offers specialized training in IT and software development with hands-on experience.\n\n5. **Codec Networks**: Known for cybersecurity and ethical hacking courses.\n\n6. **TGC Animation and Multimedia**: Offers courses in web development, graphic design, and multimedia.\n\n7. **DU (University of Delhi)**: Offers various undergraduate and postgraduate courses in computer science and IT.\n\n8. **CDAC (Centre for Development of Advanced Computing)**: Offers advanced courses and training in IT and electronics.\n\n9. **Sysinfocom**: Provides training in various IT domains including software development and networking.\n\nIt is recommended to visit the institutes, talk to alumni, check the curriculum, and understand the placement records before making a decision.",
